-- ISA Can Bid for Colombia Highway Project, Caracol Radio Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 2012-06-12T14:01:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-12/isa-can-bid-for-colombia-highway-project-caracol-radio-says.html
Colombian energy and highway company
Interconexion Electrica SA, known as ISA, can take part in a
public auction to build the Prosperity Highway, Caracol Radio
said, citing an  interview  with Mines and Energy Minister
 Mauricio Cardenas .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Bogota at 
